{"tid":1399618,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"阿叔發威~阿叔有嘢講","createTime":"2019-08-03T08:28:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T08:43:11.000Z","uid":273955,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"77bcf63fd9a8243feea895d6d71eb1c8dae7c98c","tid":1399618,"uid":273955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T08:28:10.000Z","msg":"尋晚遮打公園認識有個叔70幾歲，前輩經歷過晒香港嘅暴動，見多識廣。阿叔話後生仔發夢個時唔好掘路磚呀，破壞環境之餘，因有大有細，又三尖八角用起嚟唔就手，最重要轉移唔方便，漏低晒浪費晒，佢話點解唔考慮利用舊的高爾夫球，平靚正，質地重量都👍。用個袋裝一人帶10零廿個.....鍾意打高爾夫唔得呀！<br />\n阿叔仲介紹一項運動畀後生仔:棍網球<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Eke8zOZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEke8zOZ.jpg&h=7f60cf71&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c5gGank.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc5gGank.jpg&h=3be84068&s={SIZE}\" /> 有運動細胞嘅後生仔一睇就知道，杠桿原理可以傳送物件可以好遠又慳力。試過攞嚟玩礶裝汽水尤其快靚正，唔使濕手濕腳一pick就起，當然物料稍稍改良適應潮流必須嘅。"},{"pid":"1d075a44018f75b2df92a65cd39f472168df3341","tid":1399618,"uid":273955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T08:31:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a0d57953b1e035d68f83019ca8f992c154144a84","tid":1399618,"uid":179729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T08:32:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"55e6cd206196c0a3c5d63967612a73633a683f54","tid":1399618,"uid":70487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T08:33:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">香港警察</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\">知法犯法</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">污糟邋遢</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">一味靠嚇</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">毫無人格</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">淪為垃圾</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">吞槍自殺</span></div></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"f1e6331213c1b570ecb38ef145660a9c903ae0e1","tid":1399618,"uid":11436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite